      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 11,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "I would like to give a huge thumbs up to the outstanding service provided by the entire team of staff at Fuka Care Centre.\n\nThe whole team from the admin staff, nursing, kitchen and care giving, under the superb leadership of Mr Ong and Mr Ng, have provided excellent care and service to my father, who has been staying there since late Dec 2025.\n\nThe centre is clean, well maintained and provides a safe haven for all the residents. The overall vibe of the place is cozy and homely. Most of all, the friendly, helpful and professional staff will be a key consideration for anyone who is researching for an ideal place to care for their loved ones.\n\nI have peace of mind knowing that my father is in good hands under the personalized and compassionate care from all the staff here. They are patient and kind and will go the extra mile to support my father, especially in the initial period when he was adjusting to the new environment.\n\nThank you Team Fuka for the wonderful care given to my father. It has provided me and my siblings peace of mind as we take care of our daily obligations. We also visit and keep in touch with our father regularly.\n\nTo Team Fuka, thank you once again and keep up the good work!\n\nFor those of you who are looking for a good care facility for your loved ones, look no further. I would strongly recommend Fuka Care Centre!\n\nRegards,\nClare Tang",
      "textTranslated": null,
      "publishAt": "4 days ago",
