    {
      "reviewerId": null,
      "reviewerUrl": null,
      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 3,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "郑先生，\n在一场手术后，因需要一个安心养病的地方，来到了福家疗养中心。\n\n在这一个半月里，\n我们陪着他慢慢地康复，\n从日常照护、饮食，到每一次的关心与陪伴。\n一点一点，看着他越来越有精神、活力,我们也为他开心。\n\n三月十五日，\n他带着健康与笑容，回家了。\n\n对我们来说，\n这不只是“照顾一位长者”，\n而是陪伴一位家人，走过一段需要被守护的日子。\n\n未来若需要复诊，\n或当孩子出外公干，\n郑先生也会回来福家小住几天。\n\n福家，\n不只是疗养的地方，\n更是一个可以安心托付的“第二个家”。 ❤️",
      "textTranslated": "Mr. Zheng, after undergoing surgery, came to Fujia Nursing Home because he needed a safe place to recuperate.\n\nOver the past month and a half,\nwe accompanied him on his slow recovery,\nfrom daily care and diet to every moment of concern and companionship.\n\nLittle by little, seeing him become more energetic and vibrant filled us with joy.\n\nOn March 15th,\nhe went home healthy and smiling.\n\nFor us,\nthis was not just \"caring for an elderly person,\"\nbut accompanying a family member through a period of time when he needed to be cared for.\n\nIn the future, if he needs follow-up appointments,\nor when his children are away on business,\nMr. Zheng will also return to Fujia for a few days.\n\nFujia is not just a place for recuperation, but a \"second home\" where he can entrust his care with peace of mind. ❤️",
      "publishAt": "a month ago",
      "publishedAtDate": "2026-03-18T08:55:12.952Z",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "reviewId": "Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT200dFdFMWtRVVJaY1ZOWFMwNURlRkphUTNkV1puYxAB",
