    {
      "reviewerId": null,
      "reviewerUrl": null,
      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 2,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "感谢福家康乐疗养院:\n\n衷心感谢福家康乐疗养院在我老爸入住的 6 天\n（15号－20号）里给予的细致照顾。\n\n特别是\n在医院陪伴他的夜间看护，\n你们耐心、贴心、温柔的陪伴，让老爸在身体最虚弱的时候，仍能感受到关怀，\n这让我们家人倍感放心。\n\n那份“有人在旁守着”的踏实，对老爸来说是安宁🙏\n\n这对我们来说，\n是一种难以言语的安慰。\n\n21号凌晨 1:45am ，\n父亲因突发情况被紧急送往 JB Aminah 医院。\n虽然最终仍于 23号清晨 4:30am 离世 .\n\n但我们真心感谢疗养院在\n他生命最后一段时光所给予的用心与关怀。\n\n谢谢你们曾带给老爸\n安心与温暖。\n\n我们一家人都会铭记在心\n🙏",
      "textTranslated": "Thank you, Fujia Kang Le Nursing Home:\n\nWe sincerely thank Fujia Kang Le Nursing Home for the meticulous care they provided during my father's six-day stay (15th-20th).\n\nEspecially the nighttime care during his hospital stay; your patient, considerate, and gentle companionship allowed my father to feel cared for even when he was at his weakest,\n\nwhich gave our family great peace of mind.\n\nThat sense of security, knowing someone was there for him, brought him peace 🙏\n\nThis was an indescribable comfort to us.\n\nAt 1:45 AM on the 21st, my father was rushed to JB Aminah Hospital due to a sudden emergency.\n\nAlthough he ultimately passed away at 4:30 AM on the 23rd,\n\nwe are truly grateful to the nursing home for their dedication and care during his final days.\n\nThank you for bringing my father peace and warmth.\n\nOur family will forever remember you 🙏",
